ured</td><td valign="top">4FQ1 (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib39">Mouquet et al., 2012</xref>) (3.0)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top"/><td valign="top">Germline</td><td valign="top">4FQQ (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib39">Mouquet et al., 2012</xref>) (2.4)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top"/><td valign="top">Chimera<sup>&#8225;</sup></td><td valign="top">5CEZ (<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib24">Garces et al., 2015</xref>) (3.0)</td></tr></tbody></table><table-wrap-foot><fn><p><sup>*</sup>Single mutation reverted from bnAb;</p><p><sup>&#8224;</sup>Intermediate HC with the LC from the unmutated common ancestor (UCA);</p></fn><fn><p><sup>&#8225;</sup>Intermediate HC 3 hr with mature LC 109L.</p></fn></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap>